Name: AdGroupCount
Notes: The count of AdGroup objects using the bidding strategy.

Name: AdGroupCriteriaCount
Notes: The count of AdGroupCriterion objects using the bidding strategy or label.

Name: AverageCpc
Notes: The total cost of all clicks divided by the total number of clicks received.

Name: AverageCpm
Notes: Average Cost-per-thousand impressions (CPM).

Name: AveragePosition
Notes: Your ad's position relative to those of other advertisers.

Name: CampaignCount
Notes: The count of Campaign objects using the bidding strategy.

Name: ClickConversionRate
Notes: The number of converted clicks divided by your total clicks that can be tracked to a conversion. This is how often a click on your ad resulted in a conversion. Percentage returned as "x.xx%".

Name: Clicks
Notes: The number of clicks.

Name: ConversionRateManyPerClick
Notes: The number of conversions divided by total clicks that can be tracked to conversions. Percentage returned as "x.xx%".

Name: ConversionValue
Notes: The sum of conversion values for all conversions.

Name: ConversionsManyPerClick
Notes: This column reports total conversions, across all the conversion actions you're tracking. How you've chosen to count your conversions (unique or all) affects the number shown in this column.

Name: ConvertedClicks
Notes: The number of clicks that converted within your chosen conversion window.

Name: Cost
Notes: The sum of your cost-per-click (CPC) and cost-per-thousand impressions (CPM) costs during this period. Other costs such as cost-per-call aren't included. For a sum of all costs, use the TotalCost column.

Name: CostPerConversionManyPerClick
Notes: Total cost divided by your total conversions.

Name: CostPerConvertedClick
Notes: Cost divided by your total converted clicks.

Name: Ctr
Notes: The number of clicks your ad receives (Clicks) divided by the number of times your ad is shown (Impressions). Percentage returned as "x.xx%".

Name: Date
Notes: The date formatted as yyyy-MM-dd.

Name: DayOfWeek
Enum Values:
MONDAY / Monday
TUESDAY / Tuesday
WEDNESDAY / Wednesday
THURSDAY / Thursday
FRIDAY / Friday
SATURDAY / Saturday
SUNDAY / Sunday
Notes: The name of the day of the week, e.g., "Monday".

Name: Device
Enum Values:
UNKNOWN / Other
DESKTOP / Computers
HIGH_END_MOBILE / Mobile devices with full browsers
TABLET / Tablets with full browsers
Notes: Device type where the impression was shown.

Name: HourOfDay
Notes: The hour of day as a number between 0 and 23, inclusive.

Name: Id
Notes: ID of the main object of this row.

Name: Impressions
Notes: Count of how often your ad has appeared on a search results page or website on the Google Network.

Name: Month
Notes: The first day of the month, formatted as yyyy-MM-dd.

Name: MonthOfYear
Enum Values:
JANUARY / January
FEBRUARY / February
MARCH / March
APRIL / April
MAY / May
JUNE / June
JULY / July
AUGUST / August
SEPTEMBER / September
OCTOBER / October
NOVEMBER / November
DECEMBER / December
Notes: The name of the month of the year, e.g., "December".

Name: Name
Notes: The name of the main object in this row. For example, in a Campaign Performance Report this will be the name of each row's Campaign. In an Ad Group Performance Report this will be the name of each row's AdGroup.

Name: NonRemovedAdGroupCount
Notes: The count of non-removed ad groups using the bidding strategy.

Name: NonRemovedAdGroupCriteriaCount
Notes: The count of non-removed ad group criteria using the bidding strategy.

Name: NonRemovedCampaignCount
Notes: The count of non-removed campaigns using the bidding strategy.

Name: PageOnePromotedBidCeiling
Notes: Maximum bid limit for the PageOnePromotedBiddingScheme.

Name: PageOnePromotedBidChangesForRaisesOnly
Notes: Whether the PageOnePromoted strategy always follows bid estimate changes (false), or only increases (true).

Name: PageOnePromotedBidModifier
Notes: Bid multiplier defined on the PageOnePromotedBiddingScheme.

Name: PageOnePromotedRaiseBidWhenBudgetConstrained
Notes: Whether the PageOnePromoted strategy is allowed to raise bids if the campaign is "Limited by budget".

Name: PageOnePromotedRaiseBidWhenLowQualityScore
Display Name: Low quality keywords (Target search page location)
Notes: Whether the PageOnePromoted strategy is allowed to raise bids on keywords with lower-range quality scores.

Name: PageOnePromotedStrategyGoal
Notes: Strategy goal of where impressions will show on search result pages.

Name: Quarter
Notes: The first day of the quarter, formatted as yyyy-MM-dd. Uses the calendar year for quarters, e.g., the second quarter of 2014 starts on 2014-04-01.

Name: Status
Enum Values:
ENABLED / Enabled
REMOVED / Removed
UNKNOWN / unknown
Notes: The status of the main object in this row. For example, in a Campaign Performance Report this will be the status of each row's Campaign. In an Ad Group Performance Report this will be the status of each row's AdGroup.

Name: TargetCpa
Notes: The average CPA target set on the Target CPA bidding strategy.

Name: TargetCpaMaxCpcBidCeiling
Notes: The maximum CPC bid limit for the Target CPA bidding strategy.

Name: TargetCpaMaxCpcBidFloor
Notes: The minimum CPC bid limit for the Target CPA bidding strategy.

Name: TargetOutrankShare
Notes: Target fraction (in micros) of auctions where the advertiser should outrank the competitor.

Name: TargetOutrankShareBidChangesForRaisesOnly
Notes: Whether the TargetRoas strategy always follows bid estimate changes (false), or only increases (true).

Name: TargetOutrankShareCompetitorDomain
Notes: The competitor's visible domain URL for the TargetRoas strategy.

Name: TargetOutrankShareMaxCpcBidCeiling
Display Name: Upper Max Cpc Bid limit (Target Outranking Share)
Notes: The TargetRoas strategy's ceiling on max CPC bids.

Name: TargetOutrankShareRaiseBidWhenLowQualityScore
Notes: Whether the TargetRoas strategy is allowed to raise bids on keywords with lower-range quality scores.

Name: TargetRoas
Notes: The desired revenue (based on conversion data) per unit of spend for the TargetRoas BiddingStrategyConfiguration.

Name: TargetRoasBidCeiling
Notes: Maximum bid limit that applies to all keywords managed by the TargetRoas BiddingStrategyConfiguration.

Name: TargetRoasBidFloor
Notes: Minimum bid limit that applies to all keywords managed by the TargetRoas BiddingStrategyConfiguration.

Name: TargetSpendBidCeiling
Notes: The largest max CPC bid that can be set by the TargetSpend BiddingStrategyConfiguration.

Name: TargetSpendSpendTarget
Notes: The spend target under which to maximize clicks. Specified by the TargetSpend BiddingStrategyConfiguration.

Name: Type
Enum Values:
BUDGET_OPTIMIZER / auto
CONVERSION_OPTIMIZER / max/target cpa
MANUAL_CPC / cpc
MANUAL_CPM / cpm
PAGE_ONE_PROMOTED / Target search page location
TARGET_SPEND / Maximize clicks
ENHANCED_CPC / Enhanced CPC
TARGET_CPA / Target CPA
TARGET_ROAS / Target ROAS
TARGET_OUTRANK_SHARE / Target Outranking Share
NONE / None
UNKNOWN / unknown
Notes: The type of the main object in this row. For example, in a Bid Goal Performance Report this will be the type of the BiddingStrategyConfiguration. In a Shared Set Report this will be the type of the SharedSet.

Name: ValuePerConversionManyPerClick
Notes: The total value of all conversions divided by the total number of conversions.

Name: ValuePerConvertedClick
Notes: The total value of all conversions divided by the total number of converted clicks.

Name: ViewThroughConversions
Notes: The value, on average, of your total estimated conversions.

Name: Week
Notes: The date for the Monday of the week, formatted as yyyy-MM-dd.

Name: Year
Notes: The year, formatted as yyyy.
